rmc-sensor-tower-too-damaged = This sensor tower is too damaged to reconfigure.
rmc-sensor-tower-configure = You configure the { $name } to faction { $faction }.
rmc-sensor-tower-wipe = You wipe the faction settings from the { $name }.

rmc-sensor-tower-no-skill = You have no clue how this thing works...

rmc-sensor-tower-interact-weld = Use a blowtorch, then wirecutters, then wrench to repair it.
rmc-sensor-tower-interact-wire = Use some wirecutters, then wrench to repair it.
rmc-sensor-tower-interact-wrench = Use a wrench to repair it.

rmc-sensor-tower-interact-off = The { $name } lights up.
rmc-sensor-tower-interact-on = The { $name } goes dark.

rmc-sensor-tower-examine-weld = This one is heavily damaged. Use a blowtorch, wirecutters, then a wrench to repair it.
rmc-sensor-tower-examine-wire = This one is heavily damaged. Use wirecutters, then a wrench to repair it.
rmc-sensor-tower-examine-wrench = This one is heavily damaged. Use a wrench to repair it.

rmc-sensor-tower-examine-offline = It looks like it is offline.
rmc-sensor-tower-examine-online = It looks like it is online.

rmc-sensor-tower-repair-welder = Use a [color=cyan]Welder[/color] to repair it!
rmc-sensor-tower-repair-wirecutters = Use [color=cyan]Wirecutters[/color] to repair it!
rmc-sensor-tower-repair-wrench = Use a [color=cyan]Wrench[/color] to repair it!

rmc-sensor-tower-destroy-clueless = We stare at the experimental sensor tower cluelessly.

rmc-sensor-tower-destroy-start = You start wrenching apart the { $name }'s panels and reaching inside it!
rmc-sensor-tower-break-wrench = The { $name } beeps wildly and sprays random pieces everywhere! Use a wrench to repair it.
rmc-sensor-tower-break-wire = The { $name } beeps wildly and a fuse blows! Use wirecutters, then a wrench to repair it.
